Updated GitHub Actions pins in `.github/workflows/` and `.github/actions/` to use current releases: `actions/checkout@v6`, `actions/cache@v5.0.5`, `actions/setup-node@v6.3.0`, `astral-sh/setup-uv@v8.0.0`, `JarvusInnovations/background-action@v1.0.7`. Switched the `setup_python` composite action to rely on `setup-uv`'s built-in caching (`enable-cache: true` + `cache-suffix`) instead of a manual `actions/cache` block. Derived the `test-template` job matrix in `main.yml` dynamically from `cookieplone-config.json` via `.scripts/list_templates.py`. @ericof
